---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 191
Tags:
  - Sacrifice-Death=Humility=The Conquest of Pride
By: The Curé d'Ars
---
Humility is to the virtues what the chain is to the rosary： remove
the chain, and all the beads escape： take away humility, and all the
virtues disappear.
